conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Hey, Bailey! Long time no see. How’s life treating you?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Alex! Just grabbing coffee before work. Life’s busy but good. You?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Same here. Surviving the corporate grind. Did you finish that coding bootcamp?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Graduated last week! Now job hunting. Nerves are real.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Congrats! You’ll crush it. Still painting for stress relief?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Every weekend. My apartment’s covered in canvases. How’s your photography going?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Sold two prints last month! Feels surreal. Oh, tried that new Thai place?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Not yet. Worth it?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Spicy but amazing. We should go—my treat for your graduation.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Deal! How’s your dog, Luna? Still stealing socks?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Worse—she hid my keys yesterday. You still volunteering at the shelter?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Every Saturday. Adopted out three kittens this week!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Hero! Speaking of heroes… finally watched Starfall like you begged.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: AND? Don’t leave me hanging!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Captain Vex’s twist? Mind. Blown.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: TOLD YOU! Who’s your favorite side character?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Zara. Her backstory episode wrecked me.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Same! Though I’m salty about the Season 3 cliffhanger…

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Right? That spaceship explosion felt cheap.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Total cop-out. Writers better fix it.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Agreed. Changing topic—you seeing Maya’s wedding next month?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Wouldn’t miss it. Still need a plus-one though…

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Same boat. Let’s be awkward singles together.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Perfect. Dance floor meltdowns incoming.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Naturally. Oh! Almost forgot—my sister’s bakery needs a website. Interested?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Seriously? That’d be my first freelance gig!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: I’ll text you her contact. Pay’s decent!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: You’re a lifesaver. Coffee’s on me next time.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Better believe it. Gotta run—meeting in 20.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Go! Text me Thai place details later?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Absolutely. Congrats again, future tech star!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Thanks, future Ansel Adams!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: (Texts later) Spice Garden, 7 PM Friday? They do vegan options.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Perfect! I’ll bring my tolerance for heat… and my critique of Starfall’s costume design.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Oh, this I gotta hear. Prepare for counter-arguments about Zara’s armor.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Bring it. Also—random Q: best hiking trail nearby? Need nature time.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Eagle Ridge! 4-mile loop with a waterfall. Luna’s obsessed.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Sold. Sunday? I’ll pack sandwiches.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: You’re my favorite human. 9 AM?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Deal. Swear you won’t make me pose for photos every 5 mins?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Zero promises. My camera misses your grumpy morning face.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Rude. Remember who’s bringing the coffee thermos.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: ...I retract all sass. Hazelnut creamer?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Obviously. How’s Luna’s key-hiding rehab going?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Progress! Now she just licks them aggressively.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: [Laughs] Classic. Found a lead on a junior dev job, btw.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: YES! Details?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Startup downtown. Eco-focused apps. Interview next week.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Nailed it. Wear the galaxy-print tie. Looks smart.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Superstition? Thought you hated that tie.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: I hate how GOOD it looks on you. Secret weapon.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Aw. Thanks, man.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Always. Oh! Maya’s wedding colors are navy and gold.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Noted. I own exactly one navy shirt. Crisis averted.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Same. We’ll match. Tragic.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Coordinated tragedy. Your mom still asking when we’ll “date seriously”?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Ugh, yes. Told her you’re too busy coding world domination.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Accurate. Tell her I’m married to my paintbrushes.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: She’ll ask if they’re registered at Bed Bath & Beyond.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: [Snorts coffee] Stop. How’s your dad’s garden this year?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Tomatoes are winning. Zucchini? Apocalyptic. We’re drowning in it.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Bring some Friday? I’ll make my infamous chocolate-zucchini bread.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Infamous? Did you poison someone?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Only metaphorically. Greg from IT said it tasted “earthy.”

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Greg thinks ketchup is spicy. I’ll risk it.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Hiking tomorrow—supposed to rain. Still on?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: 100%. Waterproof gear ready. Luna’s got a tiny raincoat.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Pics or it didn’t happen.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Oh, you’ll suffer through the entire photoshoot.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Worth it for those sandwiches. Made them extra spicy.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Revenge for the Thai place bet? Low blow.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Always. Interview prep—help me mock-question?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: “Why do you want this job?” GO.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: “Because sustainable tech merges my passion for code with—”

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: WRONG. “Because I enjoy not being homeless.” Honesty!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: [Groans] You’re the worst practice partner.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: But hilarious. Real answer: “Your mission aligns with my values.” Then dazzle them.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: ...That’s actually good. Stealing it.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Trademarked! Royalties in zucchini bread.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Wedding shoes acquired. Blister-prevention plan: duct tape.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Genius. My plan: sit as much as possible.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Coward. We’re dancing to all the ABBA.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: If I must. Hiking was epic, btw. Your “spicy” sandwich nearly melted my face.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Success! And you got great shots of the waterfall.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Posted one. Got 50 likes already.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Narcissist. Tag me!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Done. Shelter busy this week?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Adopted out a senior dog! Cried happy tears.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Softie. Luna approves. How’s the bakery site coming?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Draft done! Sending to your sister tonight.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: She’ll freak (in a good way). Payment secured!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Cha-ching. Thai tonight—how spicy are we going? 1-10.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Let’s live dangerously. 8.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: ...I regret everything.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Starfall news! Spinoff confirmed: Zara’s origin story!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: SHUT UP. Release date?!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Next fall. But get this—new showrunner.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Risky. Hope they don’t ruin her.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Same. Brunch Saturday to overanalyze the trailer?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Obviously. I’ll bring my “Zara Deserved Better” mood board.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Never change. Interview tomorrow—nervous?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Terrified. What if I blank?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Impossible. Remember: galaxy tie = instant genius.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Magic tie theory. I believe it.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Text me when it’s over. Rooting for you!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Thanks, man. Seriously.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: WELL?! How’d it go?!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: THEY LOVED ME. Second interview Friday!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: [Calls] TOLD YOU! Celebrate at Thai tonight!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Yes! But spice level 6. My stomach needs mercy.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Compromise: 7. Luna demands celebration scritches.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Deal. Also... Maya’s wedding seating chart is out.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Do we sit with cool people or Aunt Carol?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Worse. Table 9: all her ex-boyfriends.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: [Laughs] We’ll survive. Bring earplugs for their drama.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Packing extra. Did you finish that sci-fi book I lent you?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: YES. Ending wrecked me. Why’d you do that?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Shared pain is real pain. My turn—recommend me something happy.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Legends & Lattes. Orc opens a coffee shop. Zero angst.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Sold. Swapping books Saturday?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Yep. Brunch, books, Zara conspiracy theories.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Thai place tonight—running 10 mins late. Luna hide your keys again?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: No, MY fault. Ironed the galaxy tie for you.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: [Laughing] You’re ridiculous. See you soon!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Hurry! I ordered extra spring rolls to sabotage your diet.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Evil genius. Table by the window?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Yep. With a view of the chili pepper decor... taunting us.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Bring it. Oh—before I forget... Pineapple on pizza: yes or no?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: ABSOLUTELY NOT. Fruit doesn’t belong on pizza!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Philistine. It’s sweet, tangy perfection!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: This friendship may not survive this.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Too late. We’re stuck surviving Table 9 together.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Fair. See you in 5. Try not to trip!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: No promises. Save me a chili!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Never. They’re MINE.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: [Arrives, panting] Made it! Where’s my tie-admiring photographer?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Here! Menu’s open to the “Dragon’s Breath Curry.” Ready?

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: ...I brought antacids. Let’s do this.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: That’s the spirit. To surviving spice—and weddings!

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: Cheers! And thanks... for everything.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Alex]
conversation_blocks.text: Always, B. Now—defend your pineapple heresy.

conversation_blocks.speaker: [Bailey]
conversation_blocks.text: With pleasure. Pass the chili flakes...
